002	EXO	028	010	Six of their names on the one stone, and the names of the remaining six on the other stone, according to the order of their birth.
002	EXO	028	011	With the work of an engraver in stone, like the engraving of a signet, shalt thou engrave the two stones with the names of the children of Israel; fitted in settings of gold shalt thou make them.
002	EXO	028	012	And thou shalt put the two stones upon the shoulder-pieces of the ephod as stones of memorial unto the children of Israel; and Aaron shall bear their names before the Lord upon his two shoulders for a memorial.
002	EXO	028	013	And thou shalt make casings of gold;
