002	EXO	028	017	And thou shalt set in it settings of stones, even four rows of stones: the first row, a sardius, a topaz, and an emerald; this shall be the first row.
002	EXO	028	018	And the second row, a carbuncle, a sapphire, and a diamond.
002	EXO	028	019	And the third row, an opal, a turquoise, and an amethyst.
