019	PSA	089	025	And I will place on the sea his hand, and on the rivers his right hand.
019	PSA	089	026	He will call unto me, Thou art my father, my God, and the rock of my salvation.
019	PSA	089	027	Also I will appoint my first-born, the highest among the kings of the earth.
019	PSA	089	028	For evermore will I keep for him my kindness, and my covenant shall stand faithfully with him.
