019	PSA	091	015	He will call on me, and I will answer him: with him will I be in distress; I will deliver him, and grant him honor.
019	PSA	091	016	With length of days will I satisfy him, and I will let him see my salvation.
019	PSA	092	001	“A psalm or song for the sabbath day.” It is a good thing to give thanks unto the Lord, and to sing praises unto thy name, O Most High:
