020	PRO	025	020	[As] he that taketh off his garment on a cold day, [as] vinegar is upon natron: so is he that singeth songs before an unhappy heart.
020	PRO	025	021	If thy enemy be hungry, give him bread to eat; and if he be thirsty, give him water to drink;
